body{

    background-color:black;
}

.page{

    color:white;
    font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    display:flex;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
}

header{

    align-self:flex-start;
    width:100%;
}

.title{

    color:red;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-align: center;
    font-size:15px;
}

nav{

    margin: top 1px;
    margin-left:410px;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    
}

a{

    text-decoration-line:none;
    display:inline-block;
    font-size:9px;
    color:white;
    margin-right:5px;
}

a:hover{

    color:red;
}


main{

    align-self: center;
    width:100%;
}

section{

    background-image: url("data:image/jpeg;base64,");
    height: 200px;
    background-size: cover;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    margin-bottom:40px;
}

section .insideSection{

    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.473);
    font-size: 25px;
    width:500px;
    padding:10px;   
    text-align:center;
    margin:auto auto;
    transform:translate(20px, 80px);
}

article{

    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom:50px;
}

.top{

    color:red;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.left, .center, .right{

    display:inline-block;
    width:170px;
    height:70px;
    background-color:rgb(34, 34, 34);
    border-radius:5px;
    padding:5px;
    margin-right: 5px;
}

.leftTop, .centerTop, .rightTop{

    color:red;
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.leftBottom, .centerBottom, .rightBottom{

    font-size:10px;
}

footer{

    align-self:flex-end;
    text-align: center;
    width:100%;
}

.contact{

    color:red;
    text-align: center;
    font-size:12px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.email{

    font-size:10px;
    margin-bottom:40px;
}

.bottom{

    font-size:10px;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);
    width:100%;
    padding: 10px;
}
